STATE BAR
v.
McGEE. No. 406P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2007.

Michael H. McGee, Pro Se.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th day of August 2007 by Plaintiff to Dismiss Petition for Writ of Certiorari:
